									<div class="post-block">
										<div class="post-block-title">Letters from the Front</div>
										<div class="post-block-sub">Posted on Friday, November 2, 2012</div>
										<div class="post-block-content">
											<div style="background: #000000 url('/images/events/letters from the front.jpg') center -180px no-repeat; height: 400px;"><span style="background: #000000; color: #ffffff; display: block; font-size: 40px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; padding: 0 30px; text-align: right;"><span style="display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 758px;">Letters from the Front</span></span></div>
											<p>The Mary Kaeser Library Readers Theatre presents <i>Letters from the Front</i>. A dramatic reading of letters sent from the people who fought in the Canadian military.</p>
											<p>Join us at the library for an evening of drama, desserts and coffee as we pay tribute those who have served.</p>
											<p>Tickets cost $15.00 each and are available at the library and the Rusty Raven. Proceeds will go to the Edmonton Valour House.</p>
											<p style="border-left: 3px solid #bdbdbd; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; padding-left: 5px; text-align: justify;"><b>Event Information</b><br />Saturday, November 10<sup>th</sup> at 7:00 pm<br />in the Mary Kaeser Library</p>
